OL,3,CThree teens detained for killing dog
OL,4,Cwalker after park row
OL,6,FThree teenagers have been detained
OL,7,Fafter killing a dog walker following a
OL,8,Frow in a park.
OL,10,FTwo boys, now aged 16 and 15, and a
OL,11,Fgirl, now 16, subjected to weeks of
OL,12,Fverbal abuse and bullying before
OL,13,Fattacking him on 26 April last year.
OL,15,FOn that day, the teens, who can't be
OL,16,Fnamed for legal reasons, carried out
OL,17,Ftheir "grave attack" at Snow Hill
OL,18,FRecreation Ground, which was filmed
OL,19,Fand shown at a hearing at Warwick
OL,20,FCrown Court.
