OL,3,CThree teens detained for killing dog
OL,4,Cwalker after park row
OL,6,FAt Warwick Crown Court on Thursday 21
OL,7,FMarch), Mr Justice Choudhury KC passed
OL,8,Fsentenced on the teenagers.
OL,10,FThe male defendants were both
OL,11,Fsentenced to a two-year detention and
OL,12,Ftraining order, with a one-year
OL,13,Fcustodial element followed by a year
OL,14,Fof supervision in the community.
OL,16,FThe 16-year-old girl was sentenced to
OL,17,Fan 18-month detention and training
OL,18,Forder, comprising nine months in
OL,19,Fcustody and nine months of supervision.
