OL,6,FThe footage showed one of the boys put
OL,7,FHackett in a headlock. At this point,
OL,8,Fthey were heard "mocking" him as he
OL,9,Fwas gasping for breath and begging to
OL,10,Fbe left alone.
OL,12,FThe attack lasted just 36 seconds but
OL,13,Fit left him with several broken ribs
OL,14,Fand a split to one of his kidneys.
OL,16,FThe 36-year-old and a member of the
OL,17,Fpublic called the police.
OL,19,FOfficers attended and spoke to the
OL,20,Fthree attackers, who all claimed they
OL,21,Fwere acting in self-defence.
