OL,4,Cwalker after park row
OL,6,FThe court was told officers went to Mr
OL,7,FHackett's house, where they found him
OL,8,Fin considerable distress and took him
OL,9,Fto hospital.
OL,11,FTwo hours later he discharged himself
OL,12,Ffrom hospital and went home, but he
OL,13,Fcollapsed the following morning and
OL,14,Fwas declared dead at the scene by
OL,15,Fparamedics.
OL,17,Fand at a previous hearing, they all
OL,18,Fpleaded guilty to manslaughter.
