OL,6,FMr Hackett's mother, Christine Smith,
OL,7,Fsobbed in court as the video and other
OL,8,Frecordings of the previous harassment
OL,9,Fand the fatal attack were shown.
OL,11,FPolice, Detective Chief Inspector
OL,12,FCollette O'Keefe said: "The level of
OL,13,Fviolence shown by these offenders was
OL,14,Ftruly shocking and Mr Hackett must
OL,15,Fhave been terrified throughout.
OL,17,F"Our thoughts are with his family who
OL,18,Fhave understandably been left
OL,19,Fdevastated by his death.
