OL,6,F"These three young people may not have
OL,7,Fintended to kill Mr Hackett but that
OL,8,Fis ultimately what happened, and like
OL,9,FMr Hackett's family, they will live
OL,10,Fwith the consequences of their actions
OL,11,Ffor the rest of their lives."
